{"tid":833400,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[拋磚]一人一個高質香港人應有嘅條件","createTime":"2018-09-23T13:23:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-23T14:44:33.000Z","uid":106431,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b496949fb93e18fc52ccfb387addc882ccc1fb02","tid":833400,"uid":106431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T13:23:21.000Z","msg":"香港呢排發生好多事。<br />\n突然諗起其實香港地都出唔少勁人，可以好高質，但近年主觀覺得整體水平跌咗<br />\n其實製造一個提升香港人質素嘅movement可唔可行？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可行<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔可行<br />\n<br />\n如題：<br />\n我心目中普遍香港人水平應該要係：<br />\n兩文三語好(支那語要識，但可以選擇唔講)<br />\n關心社會、政治<br />\n環保<br />\n支持本土（製作、藝術、運動、品牌。。。）<br />\n有國際視野<br />\n適當地可以同人社交，喺外國唔會一班香港人圍威喂<br />\n有人情味，守望相助<br />\n<br />\n巴絲們補充下<br />\nSorry for 1999"},{"pid":"cc5a36cfe98df2751b4583b9e68d9ea9d0ed9717","tid":833400,"uid":2419,"like":4,"dislike":19,"score":-15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T13:25:47.000Z","msg":"睇延禧攻略同中國有xx<br />\n玩抖音<br />\n用淘寶 wechat 支付寶<br />\n坐高鐵去飲喜茶食海底撈"},{"pid":"b1a19c2e30ba576cad12bf70a21a3286171523f8","tid":833400,"uid":8543,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T13:26:43.000Z","msg":"多元種族文化<br />\n有外國護照"},{"pid":"f39ed2b01dbc74dec484a447be9eaa89fdd57b30","tid":833400,"uid":59283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T13:26:59.000Z","msg":"唔用支那apps"},{"pid":"d80868eef7d4aea604768d0cd2e4a678c52914de","tid":833400,"uid":187076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T13:27:41.000Z","msg":"貼地"},{"pid":"c0fc69b9672d3f263002cb7e1685ce8a37dd9220","tid":833400,"uid":106431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T13:40:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇延禧攻略同中國有xx<br />\n玩抖音<br />\n用淘寶 wechat 支付寶<br />\n坐高鐵去飲喜茶食海底撈</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我鍾意你個表達方式   呢班人我無意見"},{"pid":"35af83708b99141778ac00cb475112d1090a6189","tid":833400,"uid":106431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score